lpf (0.1.3-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Multi-backend rollback with nftables, TC, routing, and sysctl restore.
  * New sysctl module with snapshot, restore, and diff support.
  * Robust conntrack delete now accepts optional sport/dport filters.
  * Integration test suite with 34 new tests for ip, sysctl, and conntrack.
  * CI man page freshness check and OCamlformat integration.

 -- lpf maintainers <lpf@example.com>  Thu, 18 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000

